      <JapaneseText>イヤ、おかしくね？
焼き魚なんざ誰が作っても一緒だろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, isn't this just ODD? This grilled fish
tastes the same no matter who it is makin' it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>つーか焼くだけじゃねェか！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heck, all you gotta do is grill the damn thing!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>で、でも一応頼まれたんだし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>B-But... we were asked if we could do it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Not sure about this in context.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>頑張ろう、スパーダ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We have to do our best, Spada.</EnglishText>
